# Safe (app.safe.global) fetches `/manifest.json` (and the icon it points to)
# cross-origin before loading us as a Safe App, so these files must be served
# with permissive CORS. `_headers` is the Cloudflare Pages / Netlify convention
# for per-path response headers; if the widget is deployed elsewhere (Workers,
# S3+CloudFront, nginx, ...) the same headers must be configured there instead.
/manifest.json
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
  Access-Control-Allow-Methods: GET, OPTIONS
  Access-Control-Allow-Headers: X-Requested-With, content-type, Authorization

/logo.svg
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
  Access-Control-Allow-Methods: GET, OPTIONS
  Access-Control-Allow-Headers: X-Requested-With, content-type, Authorization
